13 C. Monies appropriated from the fund shall be used exclusively by the
14 Department of Transportation and Development office of Louisiana Highway
15 Construction for funding projects for any road which is part of the state highway
16 system but not part of the federal system and, thus, is ineligible for federal highway
17 funding assistance. Such projects shall include but not be limited to design,
18 preventive maintenance, rehabilitation, restoration, and improvement of the
19 state-maintained system of roads. In addition, these funds may be used to complete
20 all of the preconstruction activities such as planning, survey, design, engineering,
21 right-of-way acquisition, and utility relocations associated with such projects. These
22 funds may also be used to compensate a parish or municipal governing authority for
23 the acceptance of ownership of any road on the state highway system that is not part
24 of the federal system pursuant to R.S. 48:224.1.
